<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 06:09:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管有言论，内塔尼亚胡和以色列军队都不愿意在拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/despite-talk-neither-netanyahu-nor-the-israeli-army-are-eager-to-operate-in-rafah/0000018d-b8ed-dc8c-a3df-fafdd5d20000</link><description>随着人质解救时间的临近，内塔尼亚胡的立场变得更强硬，以加大对哈马斯的压力，而哈马斯在加沙境外的领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚则要求不启动，达成协议的机会似乎正在减少</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 04:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/despite-talk-neither-netanyahu-nor-the-israeli-army-are-eager-to-operate-in-rafah/0000018d-b8ed-dc8c-a3df-fafdd5d20000</guid></item><item><title>阿尔及利亚向联合国提交加沙停火提案；美国称将反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-live/algeria-submits-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-to-un-u-s-says-will-oppose/0000018d-ba05-dc8c-a3df-fa35ad830000</link><description>以色列国家安全顾问表示，内塔尼亚胡将在“下周”制定加沙提案 ■ 内塔尼亚胡表示，拉法行动只有在平民从战区撤离后才会发生 ■ 全国各地数千人抗议，要求释放人质，要求举行选举 ■ 卡塔尔总理表示最近几天的谈判看起来前景并不乐观</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 03:50:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-live/algeria-submits-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-to-un-u-s-says-will-oppose/0000018d-ba05-dc8c-a3df-fa35ad830000</guid></item><item><title>拉法突袭中人质获释：“并非所有人质都能在英勇行动中获救”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/hostages-freed-in-rafah-raid-not-all-hostages-can-be-rescued-in-heroic-operations/0000018d-b8c5-dd5e-a59d-fdf7f6480000</link><description>数千名以色列人聚集在特拉维夫，支持在加沙被扣押的人质亲属，他们敦促内塔尼亚胡派代表团参加开罗会谈，并指责政府抛弃了他们的亲人</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 21:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/hostages-freed-in-rafah-raid-not-all-hostages-can-be-rescued-in-heroic-operations/0000018d-b8c5-dd5e-a59d-fdf7f6480000</guid></item><item><title>道路封锁、与警察发生冲突：以色列各地数千人集会反对内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/blocked-roads-clashes-with-police-thousands-rally-against-netanyahus-government/0000018d-b8ae-dc8c-a3df-fabf5a0d0000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法、贝尔谢巴和凯撒利亚的数千名反政府示威者呼吁提前选举并罢免总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 20:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/blocked-roads-clashes-with-police-thousands-rally-against-netanyahus-government/0000018d-b8ae-dc8c-a3df-fabf5a0d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家安全顾问表示，内塔尼亚胡本周将尝试制定加沙“事后”计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/netanyahu-to-try-to-formulate-day-after-plan-for-gaza-says-national-security-adviser/0000018d-b89e-dc8c-a3df-fabf31c80000</link><description>以色列国家安全顾问查奇·哈内格比 (Tzachi Hanegbi) 在接受 Kan 11 采访时表示，“我们没有兴趣管理加沙 220 万巴勒斯坦人的生活”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 20:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/netanyahu-to-try-to-formulate-day-after-plan-for-gaza-says-national-security-adviser/0000018d-b89e-dc8c-a3df-fabf31c80000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列发动战争，亲巴勒斯坦的抗议活动席卷了艺术界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/the-pro-palestine-protests-taking-over-the-art-world-as-israel-wages-war/0000018d-ad41-dc8c-a3df-ff7582180000</link><description>随着毁灭性的加沙战争进入第四个月，不同类型的战斗正在世界各地的文化机构蔓延——包括柏林的汉堡火车站、纽约的现代艺术博物馆、伦敦的苏荷剧院和大英博物馆</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 19:12:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/the-pro-palestine-protests-taking-over-the-art-world-as-israel-wages-war/0000018d-ad41-dc8c-a3df-ff7582180000</guid></item><item><title>安全消息人士称，以色列警方对阻止针对加沙援助的抗议活动持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-wary-of-blocking-protests-against-gaza-aid-security-sources-say/0000018d-b83b-dc8c-a3df-fa3fd5f40000</link><description>消息人士称，根据国家安全部长本-格维尔的命令，南区警察局长缺席了与以色列陆军参谋长就此事举行的会议</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 18:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-wary-of-blocking-protests-against-gaza-aid-security-sources-say/0000018d-b83b-dc8c-a3df-fa3fd5f40000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 134 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-134/0000018d-b82e-dc8c-a3df-fa3fce900000</link><description>拜登表示，他预计以色列不会在拉法进行大规模地面行动 ■ 高级官员告诉半岛电视台，如果不允许向加沙北部提供援助，哈马斯将冻结停火谈判 ■ 以色列最大工会主席呼吁以色列在加沙举行选举12 月 ■ 布林肯：未来几个月，以色列将有一个“非凡的机会”融入中东地区 ■ 战争结束 134 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 17:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-134/0000018d-b82e-dc8c-a3df-fa3fce900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部男子被枪杀，儿子受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-northern-israel-son-seriously-wounded/0000018d-b7e5-dd5e-a59d-f7f7f43c0000</link><description>两人在该男子的车内被枪杀，警方怀疑动机是两个月前另一名当地男子死亡后两个家庭之间的不和</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 16:46:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-northern-israel-son-seriously-wounded/0000018d-b7e5-dd5e-a59d-f7f7f43c0000</guid></item><item><title>“医生想做的第一件事就是减轻某人的痛苦。在加沙，这是不可能的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-first-thing-a-doctor-wants-to-do-is-ease-someones-pain-in-gaza-thats-impossible/0000018d-b786-dbbd-a5dd-f7c7b0400000</link><description>“加沙的灾难比我过去见过的任何灾难都要严重，”在代尔巴拉赫急诊室做志愿者的医生詹姆斯·史密斯博士在接受《国土报》采访时说道。他补充说，间接发病率的规模只有在未来才会变得清晰</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:34:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-first-thing-a-doctor-wants-to-do-is-ease-someones-pain-in-gaza-thats-impossible/0000018d-b786-dbbd-a5dd-f7c7b0400000</guid></item><item><title>前往暴行地点的旅游揭露了以色列人告诉自己的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/tourism-to-atrocity-sites-exposes-the-lie-israelis-tell-themselves/0000018d-b542-d8ee-a5cf-b7de48250000</link><description>撒玛利亚一日游和访问南部战区之间存在联系：否认以色列实际面临的现实</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 04:51:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/tourism-to-atrocity-sites-exposes-the-lie-israelis-tell-themselves/0000018d-b542-d8ee-a5cf-b7de48250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家在实验室培育睾丸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-scientist-who-is-growing-testicles-in-a-lab/0000018d-b448-d8ee-a5cf-b7dc9a340000</link><description>尼赞·戈南 (Nitzan Gonen) 博士对人们对她的工作的嘲笑并不陌生，但她对人造睾丸将能够帮助不育男性持谨慎乐观的态度</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 04:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-scientist-who-is-growing-testicles-in-a-lab/0000018d-b448-d8ee-a5cf-b7dc9a340000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡，我的兄弟没有时间参与政治”：数千人集会劫持人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-live/new-york-times-reports-israel-responsible-for-attacks-on-two-iranian-pipelines/0000018d-b4ce-d8ee-a5cf-b7de87920000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，只有平民从战区撤离后，拉法行动才会发生 ■ 全国各地数千人参加反政府抗议活动，要求举行选举 ■ 以色列国家安全顾问表示，内塔尼亚胡本周将尝试制定“第二天”提案</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 02:25:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-live/new-york-times-reports-israel-responsible-for-attacks-on-two-iranian-pipelines/0000018d-b4ce-d8ee-a5cf-b7de87920000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报：以色列是伊朗主要天然气管道袭击的幕后黑手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/new-york-times-israel-is-behind-attacks-on-main-iranian-gas-pipelines/0000018d-b468-d8ee-a5cf-b7fc74b40000</link><description>据接受《纽约时报》采访的消息人士称，所谓的以色列袭击中断了伊朗几个省份的供热和烹饪燃气供应。能源专家补充说，袭击导致伊朗日天然气产量减少约 15%</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 00:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/new-york-times-israel-is-behind-attacks-on-main-iranian-gas-pipelines/0000018d-b468-d8ee-a5cf-b7fc74b40000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦青少年正在写遗嘱，这是有充分理由的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/palestinian-teens-are-writing-wills-and-for-a-good-reason/0000018d-ad78-d070-a7fd-ff7c855c0000</link><description>当高中生阿卜杜勒·拉赫曼·哈马德 (Abdel Rahman Hamad) 从学校步行回家时，一名以色列士兵向他的腹部开枪，导致他死亡。他去世后，他半年前写给家人的一封信出现了。他是西岸许多正在写遗嘱的青少年之一</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 23:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/palestinian-teens-are-writing-wills-and-for-a-good-reason/0000018d-ad78-d070-a7fd-ff7c855c0000</guid></item><item><title>“没有游客，也没有犹太人”：战争导致拿撒勒遭遇悲惨命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-tourists-and-no-jews-a-sad-fate-has-befallen-nazareth-due-to-the-war/0000018d-ae03-d070-a7fd-fe27c73f0000</link><description>战争、恐惧和惩罚以色列阿拉伯人的呼声已经使拿撒勒的街道空无一人。没有以色列或外国游客来访，当地居民也没有心情外出就餐。酒店和餐馆老板剩下的就是希望有更好的时光</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 23:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-tourists-and-no-jews-a-sad-fate-has-befallen-nazareth-due-to-the-war/0000018d-ae03-d070-a7fd-fe27c73f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称超过 30 名驻加沙的联合国援助人员参与了 10 月 7 日哈马斯的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-says-over-30-un-aid-workers-in-gaza-participated-in-hamas-attacks-on-october-7/0000018d-b39b-dc8c-a3df-f3bf65be0000</link><description>以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特向记者展示了情报，据称该情报表明近东救济工程处员工参与了劫持平民和士兵的人质事件</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 20:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-says-over-30-un-aid-workers-in-gaza-participated-in-hamas-attacks-on-october-7/0000018d-b39b-dc8c-a3df-f3bf65be0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院拒绝南非要求采取紧急措施保护拉法免受以色列进攻的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/icj-rejects-request-for-urgent-measures-to-shield-rafah-from-israeli-offensive/0000018d-b39b-dfc6-abed-f79fb8250000</link><description>法院强调，迫切需要执行上个月种族灭绝案件裁决中概述的临时措施，这些措施适用于包括拉法在内的整个加沙地带，而无需采取额外措施</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 20:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/icj-rejects-request-for-urgent-measures-to-shield-rafah-from-israeli-offensive/0000018d-b39b-dfc6-abed-f79fb8250000</guid></item><item><title>只有提前选举才能使以色列免遭毁灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/only-an-early-election-can-save-israel-from-ruin/0000018d-b2e4-dc8c-a3df-f2f5d03b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 18:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/only-an-early-election-can-save-israel-from-ruin/0000018d-b2e4-dc8c-a3df-f2f5d03b0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 133 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-133/0000018d-b2ff-d11b-af9d-b7ffaa130000</link><description>以色列南部恐怖袭击造成两人死亡、四人受伤 ■ 拜登重申美国反对以色列在拉法的行动，除非保护平民 ■ 以色列国防军：数十名恐怖嫌疑人在汗尤尼斯的纳赛尔医院被捕 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：四名纳赛尔医院患者因停电导致氧气供应中断而死亡 ■ 战争开始 133 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 17:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-133/0000018d-b2ff-d11b-af9d-b7ffaa130000</guid></item></channel></rss>